{
  "stem": "15732.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a girl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was complaining about taxes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I cannot remember any-- there were discrimination, for instance, for a job, let's say, that we call now a public service.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In public service, they were hardly would there be-- have been Jews in public service or the administration.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- there was sifting always.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then you are on the bottom of the list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There, there was colossal discrimination.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But if there were laws in-- towards-- about discrimination, I cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember only that after the ascent of the Hitler and Hitler's men in, in Germany, the right wring in Romania started to assert itself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in 1936, there was-- we call it the Iron Fist was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a Romanian called Zelea Codreanu came sort of the power.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had a-- on the town hall, we had a very big [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How you say it in English, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Swastika, swastika, yes-- had a big swastika there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there started to be-- to come out laws that we are not allowed to speak any other language than Romanian on the street, which made most people, most Jewish people in Chernivitsi, going [NON-ENGLISH], going-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can't speak now English-- not talking.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because most people did not know Romanian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The women did not know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The men already knew a little bit to converse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But except the children, who knew Romanian in Chernivitsi-- very few.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had clients.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had non-Jewish clients that they came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He my father was self-employed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had several people working under him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had a very good clientele of non-Jews, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did not discriminate in that respect, the coming to Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
